10
00:01:52,696 --> 00:01:55,991
{y:i}Stronger. Stranger.{y}

11
00:01:56,033 --> 00:01:59,328
{y:i}Half alive and half...{y}

12
00:01:59,411 --> 00:02:02,164
{y:i}something else.{y}

13
00:02:12,716 --> 00:02:16,762
{y:i}If we are to survive,{y}
{y:i}a new balance must be found.{y}

14
00:02:17,846 --> 00:02:20,766
