16
00:02:23,894 --> 00:02:27,064
{y:i}it should be fought{y}
{y:i}by another kind of evil.{y}

17
00:03:01,056 --> 00:03:05,435
Linin' him up for you.
Port-side shot comin' up.
Steady. Here we go.

18
00:03:12,693 --> 00:03:15,487
Steady.

19
