67
00:07:28,490 --> 00:07:30,409
{y:i}Well, lesson learned.{y}

68
00:07:30,492 --> 00:07:33,203
{y:i}No such word as "friend. '"{y}

69
00:07:33,287 --> 00:07:36,498
