{y:i}- [Woman] All but the primitive side.{y}

89
00:09:42,541 --> 00:09:44,835
{y:i}[Riddick]{y}
{y:i}The animal side.{y}

90
00:09:44,918 --> 00:09:48,463
{y:i}[Woman]{y}
{y:i}All but the Furyan side.{y}

91
00:09:53,177 --> 00:09:57,931
Some of us still remember
the true crime that happened
here on Furya.

92
00:10:00,767 --> 00:10:03,437
And once you wake...

93
00:10:03,520 --> 00:10:06,273
