{y:i}Hey.! Do you hear me?{y}

99
00:10:32,424 --> 00:10:35,093
{y:i}Follow me to Spaceport Six now.!{y}

100
00:10:40,224 --> 00:10:42,226
[Growling]

101
00:11:24,643 --> 00:11:27,479
