to get this payday off my head?

146
00:14:13,896 --> 00:14:17,191
{y:i}[People Chanting, Indistinct]{y}

147
00:14:29,703 --> 00:14:34,249
{y:i}It is said the comet{y}
{y:i}always precedes them...{y}

148
00:14:34,291 --> 00:14:36,793
these world-enders.

149
00:14:38,879 --> 00:14:40,797
The Coalsack planets are gone.

150
00:14:40,881 --> 00:14:43,717
{y:i}Eight million settlers missing.{y}

151
00:14:43,800 --> 00:14:47,429
{y:i}The entire Aquilan System is gone too.{y}

152
00:14:47,471 --> 00:14:51,892
Helion Prime shares its sunlight
with all worlds nearby.

153
00:14:54,019 --> 00:14:58,732
If we fall, they fall.

154
00:14:58,815 --> 00:15:01,109
And after that...

155
00:15:01,193 --> 00:15:04,363
My God,
how do I save my family?

156
00:15:08,742 --> 00:15:11,537
{y:i}Have you heard anything I've said?{y}

157
00:15:13,830 --> 00:15:17,459
You said
it's all circling the drain...
the whole universe.

158
00:15:17,543 --> 00:15:19,503
{y:i}Right?{y}
That's right.

159
00:15:28,512 --> 00:15:30,639
Had to end sometime.

160
00:15:39,398 --> 00:15:42,609
[Arabic]

161
00:15:42,693 --> 00:15:44,653
[Arabic]

162
00:15:48,240 --> 00:15:50,242
The one you want is now here.

163
00:16:08,218 --> 00:16:10,637
And whose throat is this?

164
00:16:11,638 --> 00:16:16,310
If you cut my throat, I'll not be able to
rescind the offer that brought you here.

165
00:16:16,393 --> 00:16:18,896
Nor tell you why it's so vital
that you did come.

166
00:16:18,979 --> 00:16:21,899
The blade comes off
when the bounty comes off.

167
00:16:21,940 --> 00:16:25,569
This is Aereon,
an envoy from the Elemental race.

168
00:16:25,652 --> 00:16:28,030
She means you no harm.

169
00:16:31,909 --> 00:16:35,579
There are very few of us
who have met a Necromonger
and lived to speak of it.

170
00:16:35,662 --> 00:16:40,292
{y:i}So when I choose to speak of it,{y}
{y:i}you should choose to listen.{y}

171
00:16:40,375 --> 00:16:42,419
Necromonger.

172
00:16:42,503 --> 00:16:47,799
It is the name that will convert
or kill every last human life...

173
00:16:47,883 --> 00:16:50,969
{y:i}unless the universe{y}
{y:i}can rebalance itself.{y}

174
00:16:52,930 --> 00:16:57,267
