to someone educated in the penal system.

175
00:16:57,351 --> 00:17:00,562
{y:i}In fact, don't pretend.{y}

176
00:17:00,604 --> 00:17:03,982
{y:i}Balance is everything{y}
{y:i}to elementals.{y}

177
00:17:04,066 --> 00:17:06,068
Water to fire.
Earth to air.

178
00:17:06,109 --> 00:17:08,445
{y:i}We have 33 different words for it.{y}

179
00:17:08,529 --> 00:17:13,116
But now we have only time
to speak of the balance of opposites.

180
00:17:13,200 --> 00:17:17,079
{y:i}There is a story, Riddick,{y}
{y:i}of young male Furyans...{y}

181
00:17:17,120 --> 00:17:19,665
strangled at birth...

182
00:17:19,748 --> 00:17:21,917
strangled with their own cords.

183
00:17:23,627 --> 00:17:26,296
When Aereon told this story
to the Helion leaders,

184
00:17:26,380 --> 00:17:28,465
I told her of you.

185
00:17:28,549 --> 00:17:31,635
- What do you know of your early years?
- Do you remember your home world?

186
00:17:31,718 --> 00:17:34,179
- Where it was?
- Have you met any others?

187
00:17:34,263 --> 00:17:36,265
Others like yourself.

188
00:17:38,892 --> 00:17:42,938
- Sister, they don't know
what to do with just one of me.
{y:i}- [Knocking]{y}

189
00:17:42,980 --> 00:17:45,482
{y:i}[Man]{y}
{y:i}Open up in there.!{y}
{y:i}[Knocking Continues]{y}

190
00:17:45,566 --> 00:17:47,985
- Stand back!
{y:i}- Open up.!{y}

191
00:17:48,026 --> 00:17:49,987
They are searching houses!
Shh!

192
00:17:50,028 --> 00:17:53,031
They look for a man
who came here today.
They think he might be a spy.

193
00:17:53,115 --> 00:17:55,450
A spy?
Did someone see him
come here today?

194
00:17:55,492 --> 00:17:57,160
{y:i}Did they?{y}
{y:i}Lajjun, stop.!{y}

195
00:17:57,244 --> 00:18:01,790
{y:i}We're sure he's in there.!{y}
I will send them away.
But wait one minute, please.

196
00:18:01,874 --> 00:18:05,043
{y:i}Will you wait one minute{y}
{y:i}to save worlds?{y}

197
00:18:06,753 --> 00:18:09,464
Not my fight.

198
00:18:09,548 --> 00:18:11,800
So, you will leave us
to our fate,

199
00:18:11,884 --> 00:18:14,219
{y:i}just like you did her.{y}

200
00:18:14,303 --> 00:18:17,514
{y:i}[Man]{y}
{y:i}Break it down.!{y}
{y:i}[Banging]{y}

201
00:18:19,308 --> 00:18:20,350
Get him!

202
00:18:20,434 --> 00:18:22,769
Come. Let us try to send them away.

203
00:18:24,229 --> 00:18:26,190
{y:i}[Commotion]{y}

204
00:18:26,231 --> 00:18:28,483
{y:i}[Man]{y}
{y:i}Move it. Come on.{y}
{y:i}[Lajjun] Leave us alone.!{y}

205
00:18:30,694 --> 00:18:34,114
There is no one here!
[Cries Out]

206
00:18:34,198 --> 00:18:37,993
{y:i}[Man]{y}
Y{y:i}ou don't understand.{y}
